  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Podi Sajia was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Panadura Division Criminal Investigation Unit, yesterday (23rd) a disciple of 'Podi Sajia', who is involved in a racket led by a major drug dealer in Panadura area, was arrested with a heroin drug worth nearly five lakh rupees.",
        "The police said that two persons, aged 23 and 26, residents of Kumbuka and Rajagama areas of Bandaragama were arrested.",
        "It is stated that the first suspect was in possession of 21 grams and 560 milligrams of heroin and the second suspect was in possession of 5 grams and 136 milligrams of heroin. The suspects were to be produced before the Panadura Magistrate Court."
      ],
